{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/title_about2.png?t=1726039821\" /><br><br>Being a solo developer is great and all,<br><br>But have you ever wondered what is it like to have a bunch of women fall head over heels for you due to unexpected circumstances when all you want to do is stay home and play video games? Well, ponder no more because in this game you assume the role of a nerdy character who, thanks to some 'story development plot armor', finds himself in this exact situation. <br><br>You will go to great lengths to evade the devoted attention of those women and maintain your solitary, unattached lifestyle, all to savor the simple joy of living life on your own terms \u2013 gaming to your heart's content.<br><br>\u2018Fighting for Singleship\u2019 is an increasingly fast paced 2D high score-chasing game with various main levels, where you'll challenge yourself or even compete against your friends to see who can stay single the longest. Your goal is to score as high as possible before the women inevitably catch up to you.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/title_gameplay.png?t=1726039821\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/choose_map.gif?t=1726039821\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/choose_time.gif?t=1726039821\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/chest_reward.gif?t=1726039821\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/chest_boon.gif?t=1726039821\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/title_learn.png?t=1726039821\" /><br>Embracing the 'easy-to-learn, hard-to-master' paradigm, the game offers a steadily increasing challenge, growing more formidable with each passing minute. Stay on your toes and avoid getting caught by the pursuing women.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/title_story.png?t=1726039821\" /><br>The story unfolds through a collection of light-hearted, humorous, and brief videos that offer a deeper insight into the background of each playable map and unraveling the player's path, helping you comprehend the journey you've undertaken to elude your unhinged admirers who are so deeply in love with you. Keep your eyes peeled; you might just stumble upon a hidden ending. Who can predict what awaits?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2644130/extras/ending_image.gif?t=1726039821\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Just Married","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2644130/3e5b38eac175c19b6dc4a238600997410e40e3bb.jpg"},{"name":"Running From Your Responsibilities","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2644130/f813d8f9121c086db3b1ffb68fc6a2a1ff341735.jpg"},{"name":"You Almost Caught Me, Savy?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2644130/35d18ac5ccf0a7a5a2edbd0d035c5b53e5f52e01.jpg"},{"name":"You Will Never Catch Me","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2644130/57a31e42e5f6285ce75ce69b3c750a8838ad6678.jpg"},{"name":"Untouchable","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2644130/59e03c1f6f7b01333bd9707ca985ea28fcf4d650.jpg"},{"name":"You Will Never Take Me Alive","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2644130/aedb712b28642fae666b7dc